# AI API Route Standards
- Use the Vercel AI SDK (`@ai-sdk/anthropic`) and `streamText`.
- The model is up to debate.
- The request body will contain `messages`, `grade` (number 1-8), `subject` (string: "math" or "reading"), and `mode` (string: "explain" or "hint").
- The system prompt MUST be dynamically constructed based on the `grade`, `subject`, and `mode`. Never hardcode a static system prompt.

